	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Playing a tune on the trumpet&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;तुरही पर धुन बजाना&lt;/span&gt;): Literally means playing music on a trumpet.
	&lt;ul&gt;
