	&lt;li&gt;Here, the first sentence mentions the idea of&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;&amp;#39;human evolution&lt;/em&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/i&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The second sentence is S. It mentions the meaning of the term &amp;#39;&lt;em&gt;evolution&lt;/em&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The third sentence is Q. It is the continuation of S.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The fourth sentence is R. It&amp;nbsp;mentions the beginning of an evolution in humans.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The fifth&amp;nbsp;sentence is P. It is the continuation of R, mentioning the first formation of a living cell.&lt;/li&gt;
