&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The sentence discusses &amp;quot;The problem with purely (4)___________________ sectors&amp;quot; and states that this problem is &amp;quot;highlighted when you look at citizens&amp;rsquo; experiences.&amp;quot; This implies that focusing solely on the broad categories or a specific type of analysis of sectors is insufficient when considering individual experiences.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
